      <title>随着债务市场的不安，“完美定价”开始显现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/debt-markets-get-the-jitters-as-middle-east-tensions-send-oil-higher</link>
      <description><![CDATA[本周，央行官员关于借贷成本和中东紧张局势的强硬言论引发了债务市场的不安，信贷投资者了解到了经济和地缘政治现实。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-20/debt-markets-get-the-jitters-as-middle-east-tensions-send-oil-higher</guid>
      <pubDate>Sat, 20 Apr 2024 19:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
